addRestaurant(string).details: To simplify the code, duplication of restaurants isn't checked --> now implemented with restaurantAlreadyExists modifier

doVote(uint256).details: To simplify the code duplicate votes by a friend is not checked --> now implemented with votedAlready modifier

returns.validVote: Is the vote valid? A valid vote should be from a registered  friend to a registered restaurant
